<section class="health-section" id="dashboard"><div class="section-head"><span class="health-kicker">FOCUSED V1</span><h2>Daily value without trying to replace every health app.</h2><p>Start with the essentials, make AI proactive, and expand safely through integrations.</p></div><div class="v1-grid">
<article><span>🧠</span><h3>AI Health Coach</h3><p>Daily check-ins, mood and energy tracking, encouragement, accountability, and weekly reports.</p></article><article><span>🏃</span><h3>Workout Tracker</h3><p>Home, gym, mobility, running, swimming, steps, calories, and personal records.</p></article><article><span>⚖️</span><h3>Weight & Progress</h3><p>Weight history, BMI, waist measurements, trends, goals, and non-judgmental progress.</p></article><article><span>💧</span><h3>Water Tracker</h3><p>Hydration goals, reminders, streaks, and patterns that adjust to the day.</p></article><article><span>🍎</span><h3>Meal Planner</h3><p>Meal ideas, nutrition targets, grocery lists, recipes, photo recognition, and barcode support.</p></article><article><span>💊</span><h3>Medication Reminders</h3><p>Schedules, refill reminders, prescription history, vitamins, and missed-dose notes.</p></article><article><span>😴</span><h3>Sleep Tracker</h3><p>Sleep journal, score, bedtime reminders, trends, white noise, and calming audio.</p></article><article><span>🧘</span><h3>Mood Journal</h3><p>Stress check-ins, gratitude, affirmations, meditation, breathing, and calming exercises.</p></article><article><span>📈</span><h3>Health Dashboard</h3><p>Daily score, weekly trends, monthly progress, streaks, achievements, and next actions.</p></article><article><span>⌚</span><h3>Health Integrations</h3><p>Apple Health and Health Connect first, with Fitbit, Garmin, Samsung, Oura, and WHOOP later.</p></article><article><span>🙏</span><h3>DailyBreath</h3><p>Optional verses, prayer reminders, gratitude, reflection prompts, and wellness challenges.</p></article><article><span>🪙</span><h3>Beyond bit$</h3><p>Optional rewards for workouts, hydration, healthy streaks, courses, and community challenges.</p></article><article><span>🛹</span><h3>Beyond Skate</h3><p>Skate coaching, trick progression, safe session planning, movement goals, board design, and skill practice inside Beyond Health.</p><p><a class="health-button secondary" href="/beyond-health/beyond-skate/">Open Beyond Skate</a></p></article>
