<section class="health-section ai-panel"><div><span class="health-kicker">PROACTIVE BEYOND AI</span><h2>Helpful observations, not a generic chatbot.</h2><p>AI notices patterns and suggests small actions while keeping the user in control.</p></div><div class="insight-list"><p>“You slept under six hours three nights in a row.”</p><p>“Your water intake has dropped this week.”</p><p>“A 20-minute walk fits today’s weather.”</p><p>“Your weight trend has stabilized.”</p></div></section>
<section class="health-section"><div class="section-head"><span class="health-kicker">SAFE EXPANSION</span><h2>Future capabilities</h2></div><div class="future-grid"><article><h3>❤️ Heart Health</h3><p>Heart rate, blood pressure, cholesterol, weight, BMI, and waist trends.</p></article><article><h3>👨‍⚕️ Symptom Education</h3><p>Common symptom explanations, self-care education, warning signs, and visit preparation—with clear clinical boundaries.</p></article><article><h3>🏥 Medical Records</h3><p>Labs, vaccines, allergies, emergency contacts, blood type, family history, and secure sharing.</p></article><article><h3>🚨 Emergency</h3><p>SOS, ICE profile, Medical ID, and one-tap emergency contact calling.</p></article><article><h3>👶 Family Health</h3><p>Child growth, pregnancy timeline, senior medication support, and shared family accounts.</p></article><article><h3>🎓 Beyond Learn</h3><p>Nutrition, first aid, CPR awareness, mental health, anatomy, fitness science, and healthy cooking.</p></article></div></section>
